casebody.data:
Joseph BARTONEK, Joseph Bartonek, LLC, and Barton Nursery Enterprises, Inc., Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
TOWNSHIP OF EDISON, Township of Edison Zoning Board of Adjustment and Donna Seredy d/b/a Pretty Paws Professional Pet Grooming, Defendants-Respondents. C-522 September Term 2017
080127 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 26, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002035-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
